Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.37,0:00:20.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.74,0:00:23.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.00,0:00:29.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.09,0:00:40.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We've left the established course
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.51,0:00:44.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we're rowing straight toward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.10,0:00:49.65,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The borderline between the sky and the ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.65,0:00:55.78,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,In the dark depths of the ocean,\Nadventure holds its breath
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.78,0:01:02.58,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a good time just imagining it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.58,0:01:07.04,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.04,0:01:09.34,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:16.30,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.43,0:01:26.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"That feeling" I get when embarking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.85,0:01:30.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something I hope to remember always
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.40,0:01:35.99,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can, I won't be afraid of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.99,0:01:42.12,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,With our pulses racing, \Nlet's go on a trip now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.12,0:01:48.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Shy hearts engrave the rhythm of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.87,0:01:53.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.42,0:01:55.67,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.67,0:02:00.01,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.01,0:02:03.06,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.06,0:02:04.68,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Life is "Adventurous"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.68,0:02:06.39,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Be aware it's "Dangerous"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.39,0:02:08.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna be "One of us"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.10,0:02:09.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And a trip goes on because
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.73,0:02:11.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We da pirate of the "Mass"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.40,0:02:13.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,To the West, To the East
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.07,0:02:14.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta find my way, Sail away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.44,0:02:15.53,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,All the way to "One piece"!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.53,0:02:19.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff a dream into your empty chest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.91,0:02:22.20,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And spread your wings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.20,0:02:26.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If the wind blowing through\Nthem dyes your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.54,0:02:28.71,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's press forward
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.71,0:02:33.09,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.09,0:02:35.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.42,0:02:39.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.76,0:02:42.72,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.91,0:02:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Hot Water"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.02,0:02:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Catch!\N--That was too high!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.99,0:02:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.43,0:03:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like a Rainbow Rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.66,0:03:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get right on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.32,0:03:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'd like to give it a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.43,0:03:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.44,0:03:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to believe this resort was\Njust outside the Florian Triangle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.61,0:03:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.78,0:03:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am honored that you \Nare enjoying yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.26,0:03:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spa Island has twelve heated pools.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.82,0:03:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You're lovely!\N--There are three lazy rivers...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.49,0:03:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Incoming!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.65,0:03:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and a pool dedicated to diving.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.36,0:03:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We also have waterfalls for\Nmeditation and fifty baths,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.50,0:03:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,including a cola bath and a milk bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.94,0:03:39.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Milk Bath"\N"Women" "Men"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.90,0:03:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, we have water ping pong
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.53,0:03:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and a floating casino for those\Nwho would like to play games.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.41,0:03:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can enjoy exquisite cuisine prepared\Nby master chefs at several restaurants.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.80,0:03:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As your host, nothing could make me happier
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.12,0:03:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,than to melt away the fatigue\Nfrom your long voyage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.48,0:04:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some lucky visitors may even get to\Nsee a circular rainbow and candy rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.88,0:04:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, aren't circular rainbows
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.59,0:04:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a rare natural phenomenon \Ncalled the "ocean's treasure"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.89,0:04:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I've heard there hasn't\Nbeen a sighting in years.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.64,0:04:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I said, "some lucky \Nvisitors" may see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.57,0:04:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.52,0:04:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We might see some candy rain in just a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.02,0:04:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.18,0:04:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surely you jest!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.59,0:04:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it must be difficult\Nto run a resort on these waters.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.47,0:04:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since our opening, we've earned\N10 billion Berries a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.23,0:04:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're endorsed by the World Government,\Nso we haven't run into any problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.27,0:04:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our security is rock solid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.93,0:04:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm confident that our
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.40,0:04:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,regular guests have nothing to \Nfear as they kick back and relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.05,0:04:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,10 billion Berries a year?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.48,0:04:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally, that applies to pirates as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.68,0:04:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for your hospitality.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.40,0:05:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry if that spoiled your mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.02,0:05:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you're a paying customer,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.65,0:05:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if you're a pirate or\Npart of the Revolutionary Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.42,0:05:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two are rather similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.19,0:05:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,10 billion Berries! Berry, Berry, Berry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.83,0:05:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Slow-Slow Menace!\N'Silver Fox' Foxy Returns!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.91,0:05:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.65,0:05:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boo-yah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.35,0:05:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Whoopee!\N--Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.24,0:06:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What are those things?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.48,0:06:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Candy! It's raining candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.55,0:06:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Candy ball raindrops!\NAnd they're only raining here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.06,0:06:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.19,0:06:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're super lucky! Lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.70,0:06:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Candy too heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.53,0:06:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.14,0:06:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are so stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.39,0:06:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.86,0:06:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.59,0:06:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the ocean raccoon dog, Nukki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.13,0:06:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can transform into anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.90,0:07:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.05,0:07:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said that this girl is called Rina.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.93,0:07:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The raccoon dog talked!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.53,0:07:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a raccoon dog! I'm a reindeer!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.29,0:07:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.62,0:07:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Eh?" Be nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.08,0:07:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.37,0:07:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.99,0:07:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want my lunch? But it's not a pirate lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.35,0:07:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You're pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.15,0:07:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honest?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.27,0:07:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Luffy, the man who will\Nbecome King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.67,0:07:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the ship doctor, Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.54,0:07:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Captain Usopp, the sniper.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.61,0:07:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! I didn't know there were\Nfunny pirates like you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.99,0:07:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you! Now to chow do--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.35,0:07:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.50,0:07:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot about my big sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.54,0:08:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.40,0:08:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sis Sayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.73,0:08:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're eating up a storm!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.15,0:08:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy will eat anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.42,0:08:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ocean raccoon dogs are omnivores.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.71,0:08:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think he'll eat this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.16,0:08:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.97,0:08:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.97,0:08:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! He can transform into anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.15,0:08:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.34,0:08:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A babe! Please transform\Ninto the hottest babe ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.20,0:09:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, if only I was better with words!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.70,0:09:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Transform into Nami-san!\NPlease turn into Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.08,0:09:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're puny!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.58,0:09:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a stinking idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.35,0:09:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even if you're puny,\NNami-san is still Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.48,0:09:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.13,0:09:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.53,0:09:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? Aren't they goofy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.27,0:09:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going already?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.33,0:09:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.05,0:09:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the feast!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.58,0:10:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, are you leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.08,0:10:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Thank you for the meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.42,0:10:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.94,0:10:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a blast! Thank you, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.86,0:10:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw! Is the ocean raccoon dog leaving already?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.81,0:10:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's who you'll miss?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.88,0:10:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been looking for you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.51,0:10:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is getting old!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.91,0:10:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect you to get this far.\NYour drive is impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.78,0:10:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love to catch you here and now,\Nbut that'll have to wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.98,0:10:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've run into some rather familiar faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.95,0:10:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're doomed now that\NI've run into you, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.46,0:10:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.20,0:10:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.90,0:10:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't know who I am...\NHe doesn't remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.34,0:10:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! Boss! Don't let it get to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.64,0:11:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By any chance, are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.35,0:11:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the guy that Zoro and Sanji beat up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.60,0:11:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's doing it on purpose!\NIt has to be intentional!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.32,0:11:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.38,0:11:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Straw Hat, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.06,0:11:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You tarnished my undefeated legacy
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.93,0:11:24.49,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Fox"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.95,0:11:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and stole our pride--our Jolly Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.86,0:11:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me that you've forgotten!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.18,0:11:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Now I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.14,0:11:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Split-Head Fox!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.06,0:11:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm "Silver Fox" Foxy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.30,0:11:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, be careful. As I recall,\Nhe can shoot a weird beam.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.41,0:11:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.41,0:11:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, he isn't much of a threat\Nif we know what's up his sleeve.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.55,0:11:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't expect me to rely\Non the same tricks forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.62,0:11:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.46,0:11:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A mirror?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.72,0:11:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,High-Speed Rotation Mirror Ball Amplifier!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.33,0:11:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thousand-Armed Kannon, Slow-Slow Beam!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.77,0:12:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Shoot!\N--That's against the rules!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.64,0:12:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn... it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.35,0:12:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... told... you... so!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.06,0:12:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything struck by my beam is\Nslow for thirty seconds afterward.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.26,0:12:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be taking this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.47,0:12:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now do you remember me, Straw Hat?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.14,0:13:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll start to fall in ten seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.92,0:13:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.91,0:13:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eight!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.91,0:13:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seven!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.48,0:13:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a lovely bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.53,0:13:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It made my skin so smooth. It's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.07,0:13:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm a skeleton, so I don't have any skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.72,0:13:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you guys up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.23,0:13:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky! Brook! Beat them up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.82,0:13:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weapons Left!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.19,0:13:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.72,0:13:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.84,0:13:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cien Fleurs!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.74,0:13:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Robin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.11,0:13:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I owe ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.21,0:13:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is everyone okay? Gosh, you scared me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.26,0:14:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.03,0:14:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm a rubber man. I won't\Nlet that Slip-Head defeat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.63,0:14:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! You've added new\Nmembers to your crew, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.17,0:14:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Boss, they have a skeleton!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.14,0:14:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot! Let's try again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.24,0:14:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Victory is mine as long as \NI have this mirror ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.92,0:14:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid! What are you doing?\NShut the door already.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.56,0:14:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum Bazooka!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.42,0:15:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear I'll get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.17,0:15:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please remain calm!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.48,0:15:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Hot Water"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.09,0:15:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is everyone leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.49,0:15:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to ask you two something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.99,0:15:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.39,0:15:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about that notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.69,0:15:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Foxy and his goons are after it, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.13,0:15:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Foxy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.43,0:15:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pirates from earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.09,0:15:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, we have a history with them,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.02,0:16:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'd say they were more\Ninterested in your notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.50,0:16:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I called it, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.59,0:16:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This notebook explains how to create jewels!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.41,0:16:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How to create jewels?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.66,0:16:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Rina!\N--It's okay. Leave this to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.56,0:16:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.48,0:16:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that they're pirates, but they\Nseem trustworthy. Plus they're strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.40,0:16:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we try to deal with this on our own,\Nwe may never reach our goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.16,0:16:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, this notebook \Nbelonged to our father.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.89,0:16:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wow! It's full of numbers!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.24,0:16:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our father is an inventor, and those\Nformulas explain how to make jewels.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.93,0:16:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can read this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.23,0:16:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sis Sayo can. It goes right over my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.89,0:16:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? You're something else, Sayo-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.20,0:16:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about this? He included \Na nautical chart...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.22,0:17:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has a hot water mark and an "X."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.80,0:17:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's his secret message.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.48,0:17:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We think it's a hint regarding \Nhow to make jewels.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.11,0:17:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? This?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.74,0:17:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The formula for making\Nthem is about 99% complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.05,0:17:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he hid the remaining 1% in this clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.22,0:17:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.57,0:17:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could the hot water mark \Nmean a hot springs...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.59,0:17:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In which case, the "X" might mean Spa Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.46,0:17:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep. We reached the same\Nconclusion and snuck aboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.33,0:17:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.53,0:17:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But despite all of our searching,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.07,0:17:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we can't find anything to indicate\Nwe're on the right track.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.81,0:17:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt that notebook alone could\Ntell you how to make jewels...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.62,0:17:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the Foxy Crew has come this\Nfar in pursuit of that notebook!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.14,0:17:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might be legit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.91,0:17:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might be fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.34,0:17:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.08,0:17:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rina!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.51,0:17:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it's fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.99,0:17:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no way you can make jewels!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.59,0:17:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.61,0:18:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My father is a stupid liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.59,0:18:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is really stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.41,0:18:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate my father!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.42,0:18:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Rina and Sayo's Village\N-Three Years Ago-"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.42,0:18:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.59,0:18:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.40,0:18:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayo! Rina! This is horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.60,0:18:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.64,0:18:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a golden beetle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.50,0:18:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Legend says that our village\Nwill perish when one appears!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.20,0:18:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?! What should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.01,0:18:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.37,0:18:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The paint is coming off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.68,0:18:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He fell for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.03,0:19:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.62,0:19:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scram!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.57,0:19:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.16,0:19:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a relief! Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.03,0:19:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.06,0:19:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, isn't this great? \NThe village isn't doomed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.03,0:19:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it wonderful that it was a prank?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.63,0:19:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our father loved our village.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.12,0:19:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He loved it because that was\Nwhere our mother was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.88,0:19:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My research can save the entire village.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.13,0:19:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone will be able to live in comfort.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.53,0:19:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What type of research \Nare you conducting, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.27,0:19:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jewels! How to create jewels!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.61,0:20:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jewels...? Those aren't\Nsomething you make, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.27,0:20:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your dad sounds neat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.86,0:20:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He isn't the least bit neat!\NHe's a horrible father!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.82,0:20:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three years ago, he went on a journey\Nfor his research and never came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.11,0:20:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He abandoned us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.39,0:20:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been just the two of us ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.77,0:20:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've had to grit our teeth\Nas everyone made fun of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.22,0:20:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I don't have a dad. He's dead!"\NThat's what I've told myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.56,0:20:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then a month ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.48,0:20:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nukki suddenly came back\Nwith this notebook in his mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.37,0:20:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a letter in the notebook.\NWhat do you think it said?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.08,0:21:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Dear daughters.\NPlease complete my research."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.20,0:21:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you believe him?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.03,0:21:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was so busy with his research that\Nhe forgot about us for three years!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.61,0:21:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why must we risk our lives and\Ntravel to these dangerous waters?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.35,0:21:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's stupid! Stupid!\NI don't believe a word he says.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.92,0:21:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's fudging over his lies about\Nthe jewels with this picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.19,0:21:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did he give us this quiz at the end?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.87,0:21:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your dad really is neat!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.84,0:21:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.38,0:21:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna see those jewels.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.42,0:21:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you pay attention to a word I said?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.42,0:21:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, there you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.11,0:21:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're late, Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.62,0:21:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.19,0:21:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But didn't you come to \Nsearch for the treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.39,0:21:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't--my sister did!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.66,0:21:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm her bodyguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.66,0:22:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her bodyguard?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.90,0:22:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My sister was insistent\Nabout searching for the secret,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.97,0:22:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I came to protect her.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.11,0:22:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you guys doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.78,0:22:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am certain that there \Nis a way to make jewels!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.35,0:22:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe in him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.52,0:22:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sis Sayo...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.17,0:22:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, please help--
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.24,0:22:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sis Sayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.12,0:22:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got the girl. If you want\Nher back, do as I say!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.67,0:22:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doran?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.94,0:22:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.45,0:22:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ship's host.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.69,0:22:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.17,0:23:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like you to uncover the secret\Nbehind that notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.89,0:23:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll return the girl in \Nexchange for the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.89,0:23:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot! Foxy wasn't our only enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.33,0:23:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do, Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.47,0:23:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Rina! Finish the research.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.38,0:23:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let Dad's dream fall\Ninto the hands of that jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.59,0:23:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad's research was nothing but lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.23,0:23:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t believe Sayo got caught\Nbecause of his notebook!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.53,0:23:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Luffy! Save Sayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.35,0:23:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.73,0:23:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Great Scramble for Treasure!\NCollapse! Spa Island!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.40,0:23:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.87,0:23:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
